OL,3,CModerator of the Presbyterian Church
OL,4,Cresigns over safeguarding failings
OL,6,FThe Moderator of the Presbyterian
OL,7,FChurch in Ireland, Rev Dr Trevor
OL,8,FGribben has resigned from his position
OL,9,Fover 'serious and significant'
OL,10,Fsafeguarding failings.
OL,12,FThe Moderator announced that he will
OL,13,Fleave his post after an internal
OL,14,Freview found people within the Church
OL,15,Fhave been harmed and placed at risk
OL,16,Fdue to safeguarding failures.
