OL,3,CModerator of the Presbyterian Church
OL,4,Cresigns over safeguarding failings
OL,6,FSpeaking at a news conference in
OL,7,FBelfast, Rev Gribben said: "Following
OL,8,Fan internal investigation and report,
OL,9,Fit has become clear that there have
OL,10,Fbeen serious and significant failings
OL,11,Fin the central safeguarding functions
OL,12,Fof the Presbyterian Church in Ireland
OL,13,Ffrom the period 2009 to 2022.
OL,15,F"As a result of this, people have been
OL,16,Fplaced at risk. We are aware of a
OL,17,Fnumber of people who have been harmed,
OL,18,Fand we believe there may well be
OL,19,Fothers as yet unknown to us.
OL,21,F"We apologise unreservedly for this.
OL,26,@oD@\OUwD@AOU}D@AOU
