OL,3,CModerator of the Presbyterian Church
OL,4,Cresigns over safeguarding failings
OL,6,F"The Church's first and greatest
OL,7,Fconcern about this is for those people
OL,8,Fwho have suffered harm, and those who
OL,9,Fhave been put at risk.
OL,11,F"The Presbyterian Church in Ireland
OL,12,Fprofoundly regrets this, is deeply
OL,13,Fgrieved, and will offer all possible
OL,14,Fsupport to those affected."
