OL,3,CModerator of the Presbyterian Church
OL,4,Cresigns over safeguarding failings
OL,6,FConvenor of the Presbyterian Church in
OL,7,FIreland Rev David Bruce said issues
OL,8,Fhad emerged within the Church "which
OL,9,Fwill be of concern to many".
OL,11,FHe told a news conference in Belfast
OL,12,Fthat ensuring the "safety of all those
OL,13,Fwho take part in the life and work of
OL,14,Four congregations has long been a
OL,15,Fpriority for us".
