OL,3,CModerator of the Presbyterian Church
OL,4,Cresigns over safeguarding failings
OL,6,FHe said: "Our current safeguarding
OL,7,Fteam has identified a number of
OL,8,Fsituations between 2009 and 2021, with
OL,9,Fone as late as 2022, where we have
OL,10,Ffailed to deliver an adequate
OL,11,Fsafeguarding service.
OL,13,F"In most instances, this involved a
OL,14,Fbasic failure to follow our own
OL,15,F'taking care' guidance.
OL,17,F"These failings were magnified by
OL,18,Fmajor gaps in necessary record-
OL,19,Fkeeping, so it is inevitable that we
OL,20,Fhave not identified all situations
OL,21,Fwhere practice was unacceptable."
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOUyD@AOU}D@aO]
