OL,3,CModerator of the Presbyterian Church
OL,4,Cresigns over safeguarding failings
OL,6,FHe said this had included situations
OL,7,Fwhere the Church failed to make
OL,8,Freferrals to statutory authorities
OL,9,Fwhen required and "did not respond
OL,10,Fadequately to concerns expressed to us
OL,11,Fabout individuals in congregations".
OL,13,FHe also there were situations where
OL,14,Fthe Church failed to respond to people
OL,15,Fwho, having suffered harm, sought help.
OL,17,FHe said there were "situations where
OL,18,Fsome offenders returning to worship in
OL,19,Fchurch, following referrals to us by
OL,20,Fstatutory bodies, were inadequately
OL,21,Fmonitored".
