OL,3,CModerator of the Presbyterian Church
OL,4,Cresigns over safeguarding failings
OL,6,FRev Bruce added: "The person with lead
OL,7,Fresponsibility for this work during
OL,8,Fthese years is no longer in post."
OL,10,FRev David Bruce said the Presbyterian
OL,11,FChurch in Ireland was "truly sorry"
OL,12,Ffor safeguarding failings.
OL,14,FHe said: "Our primary concern is the
OL,15,Fpeople who have been harmed, placed at
OL,16,Frisk, or who simply didn't hear from
OL,17,Fus when they needed help or guidance.
OL,19,F"We have let you down, and for this I
OL,20,Fam truly sorry. It should not have
OL,21,Fhappened.
