OL,3,CModerator of the Presbyterian Church
OL,4,Cresigns over safeguarding failings
OL,6,F"I want you to know that we will do
OL,7,Feverything we can to both put in place
OL,8,Fbetter arrangements to prevent this
OL,9,Foccurring again, and to put the
OL,10,Fappropriate help and support in place
OL,11,Ffor you now.
OL,13,F"Anyone in our congregations, or those
OL,14,Fmore broadly associated with us,
OL,15,Feither now or in the past, who may
OL,16,Fhave been impacted can contact us
OL,17,Fdirectly."
